                <h1>Maximize Your Meetings: Mastering Zoom Waiting Rooms</h1>
                <p>The Zoom Waiting Room feature enhances security and control in virtual meetings. When enabled, participants are held in a virtual lobby until the host admits them. This allows hosts to manage attendees, ensuring only invited guests join, while also providing an opportunity to prepare or set the agenda without interruptions.</p>
